title: Arch Villain
description: A very wealthy man named Yin Wu Dao. Because of Cao’s affection for the thief, the Dragon King’s son-in-law mistreated and murdered him. However, he unintentionally activated the divine villain system, which reset his life. He must be the worst villain since he decided to be one. Shura, a legendary martial artist and the son-in-law of the Dragon King, was reincarnated as an immortal god of battle. All the proud sons of heaven, all of then go to hell!!! Arch Villain 大反派
